name: HELLBOY
description:
Hellboy spent each day contemplating the bleak molten landscape. He had long been alone; his father Diablo, fierce and distant, barely recognized him.
When Diablo left hell to go take down the 2KEYBOYS gang and the NFT world, Hellboy escaped. He longed for adventure; a life of his own away from his dark and dreary home. 
Finally, in an act of rebellion and to get his father's attention, he joined the gang that Diablo so detested.


Credits to Dahlia_Mania for part of the story.
